==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Squeezing
<hw>Squeez"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of pressing;
compression; oppression.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <pluf>pl.</pluf> <def>That which is forced out by
pressure; dregs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Same as <er>Squeeze</er>, <pos>n.</pos>,
2.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Squelch</ent>⟦br⟧
